        h1 Siena, The Tuscan Beauty

        p Italy has certainly won my heart, forever and irreversible. So much that every time I think about going on holiday
          I always think about going back there. It has so much to offer.
          For example, after visiting <a href="http://www.remindmetolive.com/stories/bridges-of-florence.html">Florence</a> I could not imagine there will
          be something else that could impress me as much. <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Siena">Siena</a> proved me wrong!
          This small town it's so well preserved, that it feels like stepping back a few centuries.

