    h2.text-center The Cathedral
    p Another sight for the eyes is the beautiful <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Siena_Cathedral">Siena Cathedral</a>.
      The facade of the cathedral is intricate and full of detail. The whole cathedral was painted, sculpted, and decorated by
      the most celebrated Italian artists of that time. It is just beautiful and I’m afraid these words and photos
      just don’t give it justice.

    p The interior is absolutely jaw dropping, yet another marvel in itself. It is like a museum, with its black and white marble
      pillars, marble floor panels, beautiful renaissance frescos, a huge bronze dome, a sculpture of St. Peter by Michelangelo.
      It definitely gives the cathedral a luxurious feel, with no expense spared in displaying the historical wealth of Siena.

